    <note>Song(2) Weigan [1584] His ancestors were the Pengcheng jun residents Song(2). He apparently moved to Kaifeng, Xianping xian. His great grandson Yu's [3812] first and second wives (sororate) were granddaughters of Yao(1) Tan [4059] (935-1009), a Caozhou, Jiyin resident, who died during his term as prefect of  Guangzhou(a) in 1009. Yu was a private scholar. Chen Shidao, WJ, 16.1a; XCB, 33.5b. CBD, 1, 775.</note>
